  <title>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Permanent Housing Reconstruction in Petit-Boucan, Gressier</narrative>
   <narrative xml:lang="FR">Reconstruction de maisons permanentes &#xE0; Petit Boucan, Gressier</narrative>
  </title>
  <description type="1">
   <narrative xml:lang="FR">Ce projet vise la r&#xE9;habilitation durable de la zone rurale montagneuse de Gressier, fortement touch&#xE9;e par le s&#xE9;isme du 12 janvier 2010, en r&#xE9;alisant la reconstruction de 400 maisons permanentes, parasismiques et r&#xE9;sistantes aux ouragans ainsi que des infrastructures compl&#xE9;mentaires (latrines et structures de captage des eaux de pluie).</narrative>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">This project aims to sustainably rehabilitate the rural mountainous area of Gressier, which was hard hit by the January 12, 2010 earthquake, by carrying out the reconstruction of 400 permanent, earthquake and hurricane resistant houses, as well as complementary infrastructure (latrines and structures to capture rainwater).</narrative>
  </description>
